sub_title: Graduated master chemistry, looking for PhD position
summary:
Bachelor in pharmaceutical sciences (VU Amsterdam) and master in chemistry (VU/UvA joint degree). Currently doing a PhD in chemical biology at the university of Leiden under supervision of dr. Stephan Hacker.

You are welcome to reach out to me via LinkedIn message or by emailing to marnixroseboom@hotmail.com.
